drawing page</A>.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.mpi-fg-koeln.mpg.de/~lk/">Gallery
of social structures</A>, L. Krempel, Max-Planck-Inst. K�ln.
Graph drawing applications in sociology.
<P>
<li><a href="http://www.graphdrawing.org/">Graphdrawing.org</a>
clearinghouse for graph drawing research.
<p>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.brown.edu/people/rt/gd.html">Graph
Drawing</A>, Roberto Tamassia, Brown U.
This page contains pointers to a
long annotated bibliography, a graph drawing tutorial, and
information on the annual Graph Drawing conference.
<P>
<LI>Graph Drawing:<BR>
<A HREF="ftp://ftp.cs.brown.edu/pub/gd94/gd-92-93/">
GD '92 and '93 reports, programs, and proceedings</A>
(TeX and PS formats).<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.inf.uniroma3.it/calendar/gd97/">GD
'97</A>, Rome, Sept. 1997.<BR>
